 * |   ↓AltF4 ↓  -  ↓   +  ↓   |      |                |      |  ↓---"--↓--'--↓---Å---↓   |  |      |      |      |      |      | |      |  ↓----Windows lock-----↓  |
 * |      |     /   /  /   /   |      |                |      |      |   \   \     |      |  |      |      |      |      |      | |      |      |      |      |      |
