 * |  11  |  12  |  13  |  ↓MyComp↓   |                |      |      |      |  19  |      |  |      |  ↓-Numpad toggle-↓ |      | |      |  ↓----Windows sleep----↓  |
 * |      |  \   \  \   \      |      |                |      |     /   /  /   /   |      |  |  ↓---------BASE---------↓ |      | |      |      |      |      |      |
 * |------+---\ [ \--\ ( \ ----+------|                |------+----/ ) /--/ ] /----+------|  |------+------+------+------+------| |------+------+------+------+------|
